  <num>47-2323</num>
  <heading>Assessments for street paving — Generally.</heading>
  <text>Assessments in accordance with existing law shall be made for paving and repaving roadways, where such roadways are paved or repaved, with funds derived from the collection of the tax on motor vehicle fuels.</text>
  <annotations>
    <annotation type="History">Mar. 3, 1926, 44 Stat. 167, ch. 44, § 1</annotation>
